title: The Steve Wilkos Show 05.26.08
description:
AUDIENCE INTERVENES:
    --------------------
    Helen is 5 months pregnant with her second child and has a boyfriend that abuses her verbally and physically. Helen got rid of her first child because her boyfriend abuses her, and now wants Steve to help her boyfriend Carlos. Carlos admits that he has a drinking problem, and wants to fix it but doesn&#039;t like going to alcoholics anonymous meetings. Steve asks the audience for their stories in hopes that Helen can see that she is not in a good relationship. Steve doesn&#039;t think that Helen and Carlos really deserve his help, but does he sympathize with their unborn child and offer to help them?

ENJOY PLEASE SEED AND SAY THANK YOU
      ------
